OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1783684141
OL,3,CCCTV released in search for missing
OL,4,Cteenager
OL,6,FA CCTV image has been released by
OL,7,Fpolice continuing to search for a
OL,8,Fteenager missing from Margate.
OL,10,FRuby Morris was last seen in the town
OL,11,Fat around 2.30pm on Saturday 27 June
OL,12,F2026.
OL,14,FThe 15 year old is described as white
OL,15,Fand around 5ft tall with long, dark
OL,16,Fbrown hair and green eyes. She has
OL,17,Fboth sides of her nose pierced.
OL,19,FA CCTV image has been released showing
OL,20,FRuby at St Pancras station in central
OL,21,FLondon at around 10.30pm that night.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
