OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1783684141
OL,3,CCCTV released in search for missing
OL,4,Cteenager
OL,6,FRuby may be wearing a long sleeved
OL,7,Fblack jacket, grey jogging bottoms,
OL,8,Fwhite Crocs and carrying a black
OL,9,Fshoulder bag.
OL,11,FDetective Superintendent Keith Taylor
OL,12,Ffrom Kent Police said, "Since Ruby was
OL,13,Freported missing we have completed
OL,14,Fextensive enquiries, including
OL,15,Ffollowing up on reports of potential
OL,16,Fsightings, searching areas to where
OL,17,Fshe is known to travel, reviewing
OL,18,FCCTV, analysing mobile phone data and
OL,19,Fspeaking with her friends and
OL,20,Fassociates.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
