PN,38903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1783684141
OL,3,CCCTV released in search for missing
OL,4,Cteenager
OL,6,FRuby is known to use the rail network
OL,7,Fand we have obtained a CCTV image
OL,8,Fshowing her at St Pancras. We further
OL,9,Fbelieve she was in the vicinity of
OL,10,FEuston station, shortly before 11pm on
OL,11,F27 June.
OL,13,FShe has connections to Birmingham and
OL,14,FWalsall in the West Midlands, Plymouth
OL,15,Fin Devon, Crawley in West Sussex and
OL,16,Fareas of London including Camden and
OL,17,FWestminster."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
