PN,38904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1783684141
OL,3,CCCTV released in search for missing
OL,4,Cteenager
OL,6,FIt may be that Ruby has been
OL,7,Ftravelling with someone known to her.
OL,8,FWe know she has previously travelled
OL,9,Fwith a woman described as white,
OL,10,Faround 5ft 8in tall and of very slim
OL,11,Fbuild, with short auburn hair that is
OL,12,Fcropped very short at the sides."
OL,14,FAnyone with critical information
OL,15,Fregarding the whereabouts of Ruby
OL,16,Fshould call 999. If people have any
OL,17,Fother information to help find her
OL,18,Fthey are asked to call 101 or use the
OL,19,Flive chat function on the Kent Police
OL,20,Fwebsite.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/4
